<designrules name="pcb-devboards_35µmCU_200µm_Strukturen_Abstaende *">
<description language="de">








pcb-devboards.de Standard DRU-File.

Bohrungen NDK+DK: 0,3 - 6,3mm (in 0,1mm Schritten)
Ab 6,3mm werden die Bohrungen gefräst, daher die Bohrung mit Umriss-Layer zeichnen.

Leiterplatten Dicke: 0,5 - 1,6mm
Kupferstärke: nur 35µm
Struktur/Abstand/Restring umlaufend: 200µm
</description>
<description language="en">








&lt;b&gt;EAGLE Design Rules&lt;/b&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
The default Design Rules have been set to cover
a wide range of applications. Your particular design
may have different requirements, so please make the
necessary adjustments and save your customized
design rules under a new name.</description>
